Actor Idris Elba who fans are voting to be the next James Bond has gotten the job to host the 2018 FIFA Best Awards. The award show will be co-hosted by French Television presenter Anne-Laure Bonnet. Cristiano Ronaldo wins the 2017 Best Men’s Player. Photo China Daily The men’s award contenders are: Juventus‘ Cristiano Ronaldo, Liverpool‘s Mohamed Salah and Real Madrid‘s Luka Modric. The women contenders are the Lyon pair Ada Hegerberg and Dzsenifer Marozsan and Brazilian legend Marta.